        "accordion_item_1": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Safety",
            "answer": "<p>Avoid using the earphones in situations where hearing your surroundings is important, such as driving, biking, or walking near traffic.<br/><br/>Keep the product and its accessories out of reach of children. Small parts and cords can pose choking or strangulation hazards.<br/><br/>Always ensure ear tips are firmly attached before inserting the earphones. If a tip becomes lodged in the ear, seek immediate medical assistance.<br/><br/>Stop use and consult a professional if you experience irritation, discomfort, or excessive earwax buildup.<br/><br/>Do not disassemble or modify the device. Avoid applying excessive force or pulling on the cable to prevent damage.</p>"
          }
        },
